=left class=m><span class=title> Re: hrm...</span><hr size=1> The whole reason they changed the quest was because having a PH turn-in spawn didn't work.  ClericA would turn-in the pearl, then both guilds would attack and ClericB's guild would get the kill and the epic.  Since the pearl was eaten by the turn-in, ClericA had to start the whole quest over.<br>
<br>
Perma-root, can summon, and unmezzable/charmable works pretty good.  How about non-kos, untargetable, melees like the Sleeper, and deathtouches?  Hand him the new pearl and HE HANDS IT BACK before he spawns the dragon.  /dusts hands<br>
<br>
Now the real issue is that the spawn time is 0-72 hours.  Make the spawn time something like 0-18 hours so you could reasonably camp it in a single day, but limit the time between spawns to something like 4 days.  Your entry of epics into the server is relatively unchanged, and people don't have to dedicate more than a single day to the camp.  <br>
<br>
My theory: Well rested people are much less pissy.<br>
<br>
Basenji, Unconquered Bard <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ushyv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shyv</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/18/02 2:17:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23352.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: hrm...</span><hr size=1> No, that's not why they changed the spawn.  It's log verifiable who handed in the pearl and who looted the heart.  Very few people can get away with doing that without having their epic yanked.<br>
